'''''Hiwassee Dam High School''''' (HDHS) in [[Murphy, North Carolina|Murphy]], [[North Carolina]] serves grades 9-12 and is one of only three high schools in the [[Cherokee_County_(North_Carolina)_School_District|Cherokee County School District]]. As of 2007 it had an active enrollment of 209 students and a full time teaching staff of 20 teachers giving an average of 11 students per teacher.<ref>[http://cherokeecounty.nc.schoolwebpages.com/education/school/school.php?sectionid=41& Hiwassee Dam High Webpage]</ref><ref>[http://www.psk12.com/rating/USindivphp/SchID_302331.html Hiwassee Dam High School Statistics]</ref>
